"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Life is the endless sea, man is a leaf boat on the sea. The sea is not calm, so people are always happy and sad. When unknown troubles hit, frustrated and hesitation burning every nerve. But, friend, don't forget to keep a quiet heart, the pain will no longer have.\\nIn front of everyone, there is a road leading to the distance, rugged but full of hope. Not everyone can go far, because there are always people because they did not dump the sand in their shoes and tired and give up halfway. Therefore, it is not pleasure and pain per se that govern human experience, but mood.\\nWhen the troubles of life hit, please leave the load, look up at the bright, blue sky, let the soft blue reflect into your heart. As a child to play tired, looking for a piece of green soft grass to lie down, let the sun jump on the face, let the breeze blowing no wrinkles of the heart.\\nWhen layers of frustration surrounded, please open the window, let the fresh air come in, in the fragrance of the sweet earth breath to find a ray of peace, just like childhood, picked up the dandelion beard, plucked up two cheeks to blow open a small umbrella, with a surprise to close your eyes, make a wish. Thus, the heart will be more than a comfort and joy.\\nWhen helpless melancholy comes, please wipe your eyes, watch the setting sun, listen to insects singing birds. As a child in the small courtyard to listen to crickets chirping, looked up to the twinkling stars in the sky. Thus, all the disturbing noise gradually disappeared, with a quiet heart.\\nKeep a quiet heart, you will sincerely sigh: even if I am not happy, do not lock the brow deep, life is short, why also cultivate bitter:\\nKeep a quiet heart, you will understand that broadness can dilute sorrow, quiet can disperse confusion. Yes, no one knows how far away it is, but open the window of your heart and let in the happy sunshine and moonlight, and the quiet heart will have an unquenchable happy song.\\nKeep a quiet heart, you can go beyond, constantly self challenge. Even if the distance is forever place, also can be born a thing - a miracle.\",\"timestamp\":1640792424,\"title\":\"Keep a quiet heart\"},\"digest\":\"bWcf7BflcVXLouwje057-3CNyOx4syoA0Z_pNWq15d8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xEE6B7a44d790a125C0fA574e113DC7D9b0d7722C\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DpD65Vj-4tpe-PFGUIewkP0vP523-L8NW7AyG8uWamg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"BCYZbtPwRf-0b2yuQLvnKuJGUmWAeIG03Thtlt4nNKY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"IsP32BrJLfLzlOMB32rMTOkFIE3TbKZYVDIaWxw-8SURDLLQDNm1NkcKc-k2rDc6kVbV4r39-QcUpe9gAwFxJw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xca442ea2479470de2a2c21e5a3c59901bebf90cb893040a8eb945f054d46b44b759d23f07c1cf4b0f37fdf438340a99abd4cd3213928853c2030c5c3e77a385e1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DpD65Vj-4tpe-PFGUIewkP0vP523-L8NW7AyG8uWamg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"BCYZbtPwRf-0b2yuQLvnKuJGUmWAeIG03Thtlt4nNKY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"bWcf7BflcVXLouwje057-3CNyOx4syoA0Z_pNWq15d8\"}"